          Indicates the outcome of the operation. For example: "200" for success, "400" for bad requests, etc.

        • message
          Collection<String> message
          The collection of messages associated with the response.

          Typically used to provide additional information about the operation's result. Example: ["Operation successful", "Additional details..."]

          The type of the response.

          Indicates the general nature of the response, such as RESULT or ERROR.
